                    <h1 class="c-article-title" data-test="article-title" data-article-title="">Adaptive federated learning for resource-constrained IoT devices through edge intelligence and multi-edge clustering</h1>
                    <ul class="c-article-author-list c-article-author-list--short" data-test="authors-list" data-component-authors-activator="authors-list"><li class="c-article-author-list__item"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" data-track-index="1_7" data-track-context="researcher popup with no profile" href="#auth-Fahad_Razaque-Mughal-Aff1" data-author-popup="auth-Fahad_Razaque-Mughal-Aff1" data-author-search="Mughal, Fahad Razaque">Fahad Razaque Mughal</a><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff1">1</a></sup>, </li><li class="c-article-author-list__item"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" data-track-index="2_7" data-track-context="researcher popup with no profile" href="#auth-Jingsha-He-Aff1" data-author-popup="auth-Jingsha-He-Aff1" data-author-search="He, Jingsha">Jingsha He</a><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff1">1</a></sup>, </li><li class="c-article-author-list__item c-article-author-list__item--hide-small-screen"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" data-track-index="3_7" data-track-context="researcher popup with no profile" href="#auth-Bhagwan-Das-Aff2" data-author-popup="auth-Bhagwan-Das-Aff2" data-author-search="Das, Bhagwan" data-corresp-id="c1">Bhagwan Das<svg width="16" height="16" focusable="false" role="img" aria-hidden="true" class="u-icon"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#icon-eds-i-mail-medium"></use></svg></a><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff2">2</a></sup>, </li><li class="c-article-author-list__item c-article-author-list__item--hide-small-screen"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" data-track-index="4_7" data-track-context="researcher popup with no profile" href="#auth-Fayaz_Ali-Dharejo-Aff3" data-author-popup="auth-Fayaz_Ali-Dharejo-Aff3" data-author-sea